# §1 end-to-end PPO ablations (circle, viviani naive + 4M, slow, v2) and
# §4 noise-color pink-trained variant. Best/best_model.zip + ppo_panda_final.zip
# for each so `eval.py --config <name>` reproduces RESULTS.md numbers without
# retraining. Small configs (net_arch=[64,64], ~206 KB each) and the two
# larger ones (net_arch=[256,256], ~2 MB each) add ~10 MB total.
